This is a free extension for Magento 2.1.x developed by igor Ludgero Miura. This extension provides the feature to add social share links in product view page.

**Installation**

To install you can download this repository and copy to your root installation, or install using the Magento Marketplace (search by the extension name).
 To install using composer type "composer require igorludgero/socialshare".

**Configuration**

When you install this extension you will have in you admin panel a link to the extension settings.

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Click in &quot;Configure links&quot; to access the settings.

In the settings page you can enable/disable all social share links you need to show in product view page and set the exhibition order.

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Save your settings and now you can see the buttons on product view page.

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)
